{"tid":945729,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃鳳嫺：支那所謂「共享單車」(出租單車)投訴增至198宗　主要涉有公司倒閉","createTime":"2018-12-18T06:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T06:09:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a7194c2ac460d2000b3e72f71866a2f2844d4c11","tid":945729,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T06:09:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1433820-20181218.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1433820-20181218.htm&d=%2F8IpAWi2c54X29EX9Mi5WpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=29f0abad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1433820-20181218.htm&h=96b972db\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1433820-20181218.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1433820_1_L_20181218103041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1433820_1_L_20181218103041.jpg&h=d179179b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消委會總幹事黃鳳嫺表示，去年收到8宗關於共享單車的投訴，今年則增至198宗，其中近一半和一間共享單車公司倒閉有關，投訴主要關於取消戶口希望退回按金、未能使用單車和客戶服務熱線無人接聽。她呼籲共享單車公司若要做好服務，要注意這些細節。<br />\n<br />\n黃鳳嫺在本台節目《千禧年代》又表示，今年有一間共享單車公司倒閉，消費者是無抵押的債權人，只可向破產公司登記，在賠償次序排到最後。黃鳳嫺認為如果未能退回充值額，對消費者是很不公平。"}]}